ine-break\"></div>\n<div class=\"main-text-body primary-black\" style=\"padding-bottom: 20px;\">\n<p>Acqua Vatos Hotel is ideally located in the heart of the coastal village of Kamari that lies on the southeastern part of the island of Santorini and enjoys the privilege of a three kilometers long black sand beach.</p>\n<p>The Acqua Vatos is not only a few passes away of the famous Kamari Beach, but is found among a great variety of shops, restaurants, cafes, bars and nightclubs and is designed to offer to its guests all the comforts for an unforgettable stay in one of Santorini’s hotspots.</p>\n<p>The village of Kamari is a perfect choice for those wishing to combine a sun &amp; beach vacation during the day and the breathtaking views and magical sunset within easy reach in the late afternoon hours since it is only 7 kilometers away from the Caldera and with a great public transport service (The bus stop is just outside the hotel’s main entrance!).</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"primary-dark title-case-secondary text-left\">Address</div>\n<div class=\"line-break\"></div>\n<div class=\"main-text-body primary-black\" style=\"padding-bottom: 20px;\">Acqua Vatos Hotel Santorini, Central Road of Kamari Village, Santorini 847 00</div>\n","css":{"element":"div","class":"animation--up","color":"primary-dark"}}]}]},"4":{"wrapper":{"fluid":true,"css":{"border":"0","backgroundColor":"#FFFFFF"},"rows":[{"css":{"padding":"80px 0 0 0","border":"0"},"columns":{"sizes":["col-md-12 animation--up"]}}]},"rows":[{"columns":[{"mapSettings":{"lat":36.3772613,"lng":25.4817143,"center":[36.3772613,25.4817143],"zoom":12},"mapStyle":{"height":"500px"},"css":{"element":"div","class":"animation--up","color":"primary-dark"}}]}]},"5":{"wrapper":{"fluid":true,"css":{"border":"0","backgroundColor":"#04456D"},"rows":[{"css":{"padding":"80px 0 60px 0","border":"0","maxWidth":"1440px","margin":"0 auto"},"columns":{"sizes":["col-md-12  animation--up"]}}]},"rows":[{"columns":[{"text":"MORE HOTELS","link":{"